YPanel Source Code Availability (AGPLv3 Section 6)

This npm package contains compiled/minified code (non-source form).

The Corresponding Source code (TypeScript, Vue, and CSS source files) is freely
available under AGPL-3.0-or-later at:

    https://github.com/cygbs/YPanel

To build from source:

    git clone https://github.com/cygbs/YPanel.git
    cd YPanel
    npm install
    npm run build

The source code will remain available at the above URL for at least three years
after the last distribution of this package.
